snippet.title: TEKKEN 8 - Story & Gameplay Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Father. Son. Mother. This family reunion is going to be explosive. 
TEKKEN 8 is bringing back old grudges to the new generation – Kazuya, Jin, Paul, King, Law, Lars, Jack-8 and…the return of Jun Kazama! 

Get ready for the next-gen battle and look forward to a lot more in the next edition of Tekken – old and new! 

Join the official TEKKEN server 👉 https://discord.gg/tekkenofficial

Get more information about TEKKEN 8 👉 https://bnent.eu/YTTekken8

Follow us on:
Web: https://www.bandainamcoent.eu
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/tekken/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TEKKEN
